ley]])\n* 2434 ([[RAF Church Fenton|Church Fenton]])\n* 2487 ([[Easingwold]])\n*:2487DF ([[RAF Linton-on-Ouse]])\n* 2527 ([[Lawnswood]])\n}}\n\n=== Cumbria & Lancashire Wing ===\n;Formerly Cumbria and North Lancashire Wing, merged with East Lancashire Wing in 2011\n;Wing HQ Inskip\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* 92 ([[Chorley]])\n* 128 ([[Barrow-in-Furness|Barrow in Furness]])\n* 143 ([[Longridge]]) - formerly 341DF\n* 177 ([[Blackpool International Airport|Blackpool Airport]])\n* 206 ([[Thornton-Cleveleys|Thornton Cleveleys]])\n* 341 (City of [[Preston, Lancashire|Preston]])\n* 345 (City of [[Lancaster, Lancashire|Lancaster]])\n* 352 ([[Burnley]])\n* 455 ([[Morecambe]] & [[Heysham]])\n* 471 ([[Hesketh Bank]] & [[Tarleton]])\n* 723 ([[Wigan]])\n* 967 ([[Warton, Fylde|British Aerospace Warton]])\n* 1030 ([[Whitehaven]])\n* 1035 ([[Accrington]] & District)\n* 1104 ([[Borough of Pendle|Pendle]])\n* 1127 ([[Kendal]])\n* 1247 ([[Penrith, Cumbria|Penrith]])\n* 1262 ([[Blackburn]])\n* 1264 ([[Windermere, Cumbria (town)|Windermere]])\n*:1264DF ([[Millom]]) - Disbanded 2018\n* 1301 ([[Fleetwood]])\n* 1471 ([[Horwich]])\n* 1862 (City of [[Carlisle, Cumbria|Carlisle]])\n* 1969 ([[Rossendale]])\n* 2050 ([[Leyland, Lancashire|Leyland]])\n* 2192 ([[Appleby Grammar School]])\n* 2199 ([[Workington]])\n* 2223 ([[Ulverston]])\n* 2246 ([[Carnforth]])\n* 2376 ([[Bamber Bridge]])\n* 2454 ([[Unity Academy Blackpool|North Blackpool]])\n* 2459 ([[Poulton-le-Fylde]])\n* 2486 ([[Lytham St Annes]]) - Disbanded 2019\n}}\n\n=== Durham & Northumberland Wing ===\n;Wing HQ Knightsbridge, Gosforth, Newcastle upon Tyne\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* 36 ([[Hetton-le-Hole]])\n* 111 ([[Sunderland]])\n* 131 (City of [[Newcastle-upon-Tyne|Newcastle]])\n* 224 ([[Hexham]])\n* 234 (City of [[Durham, England|Durham]])\n* 242 ([[Cramlington]])\n* 324 ([[South Shields]])\n* 346 ([[Tynemouth]])\n* 361 ([[Gateshead]])\n* 404 ([[Morpeth, Northumberland|Morpeth]])\n* 473 ([[Hartlepool]])\n* 607 (Wearmouth) fo