on]]\n\n=== Highland Wing ===\n;Wing HQ [[RAF Lossiemouth]], Moray\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* 52 ([[Aviemore]])\n* 161 (1st Highland)\n*:161DF ([[Ullapool]])\n* 379 (County of [[Ross, Scotland|Ross]])\n* 423 ([[Elgin, Moray|Elgin]])\n*:423DF ([[Strathspey, Scotland|Speyside]])\n* 446 ([[Forres]])\n* 832 ([[Wester Ross]])\n* 1068 ([[Nairn]])\n* 1285 ([[Caithness]])\n* 1730 ([[Lochaber]])\n* 1731 ([[Isle of Lewis]])\n* 1769 ([[Thurso]] & District)\n*:1769DF ([[Orkney]])\n* 2405 ([[Dingwall]])\n* 2521 ([[Oban]] High School)\n}}\n\n=== North East Scotland Wing ===\n;Wing HQ [[Gordon Barracks]], Aberdeen\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* 102 ([[Aberdeen Airport]])\n* 107 ([[Aberdeen]])\n* 865 ([[Portlethen]])\n* 875 ([[Westhill, Aberdeenshire|Westhill]])\n* 877 ([[Inverurie]])\n* 1295 ([[Peterhead]])\n* 1296 ([[Turriff]])\n* 1297 ([[Stonehaven]])\n* 1298 ([[Huntly]])\n* 1383 ([[Fraserburgh]])\n* 1990 ([[Ellon, Aberdeenshire|Ellon]])\n* 2231 ([[Forfar]])\n* 2288 ([[Montrose, Angus|Montrose]])\n* 2365 ([[Brechin]])\n* 2367 ([[Banchory]])\n* 2422 ([[Arbroath]])\n* 2449 ([[Carnoustie]])\n* 2489 ([[Bridge of Don]])\n}}\n\n=== South East Scotland Wing ===\n;Wing HQ [[Leuchars Station]]\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* 38F ([[Perth, Scotland|Perth]])\n* 132 ([[North Berwick]])\n* 142 ([[Trinity, Edinburgh|Trinity]])\n* 287 ([[Stenhouse, Edinburgh|Stenhouse]])\n* 297 ([[Musselburgh]])\n* 383 ([[Alloa]])\n* 439 ([[Linlithgow]])\n* 571 ([[Cupar]])\n* 775 ([[Burntisland]])\n* 859 ([[Dalgety Bay]])\n* 869 ([[Penicuik]])\n* 870 ([[Dreghorn]])\n*:870DF ([[Gilmerton]])\n* 1007 ([[Duns]])\n* 1019 (City of [[Stirling]])\n* 1143 (8th Edinburgh) aka 1143 ([[Portobello, Edinburgh|Portobello]]) Sqn\n* 1145 ([[Dunfermline]])\n*:1145DF ([[Kinross]])\n* 1192 ([[Kirkcaldy]])\n* 1232 (City of [[Dundee]])\n* 1370 ([[Leven, Fife|Leven]])\n* 1716 ([[Roxburgh]])\n*:1716DF ([[Kelso, Scottish Borders|Kelso]])\n* 1739 (2nd [[Midlothian]])\n* 1743 ([[Crieff]])\n* 1756 ([[Broxburn, West Lothian|Broxburn]])\n* 2163 ([[Auchtermuchty]])\n* 2180 ([[Galashiels]])\n* 2284 ([[Dunblane]])\n* 2311 ([[Glenrothes]])\n* 2345 ([[Leuchars]])\n* 2435 ([[St Andrews]])\n* 2450 ([[Dundee]])\n* 2463 ([[Currie]] & [[Balerno]])\n* 2466 ([[Loanhead]])\n* 2519 ([[Strathmore, Angus|Strathmore]])\n* 2535 ([[Livingston, West Lothian|Livingston]])\n}}\n\n=== West Scotland & Northern Ireland Wing ===\n;Wing HQ Paisley Cadet Centre\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n;West Scottish Squadrons\n* 32F (1st Scottish)\n* 49F ([[Greenock]] ([[MacRobert baronets|MacRoberts Reply]]))\n* 62 (2nd [[Glasgow]])\n* 122 (5th [[Glasgow]])\n* 137 ([[Ayr]] & [[Prestwick]])\n* 327 ([[Kilmarnock]])\n* 396 ([[Paisley, Renfrewshire|Paisley]])\n* 449 ([[Lanark]])\n* 470 ([[Falkirk]])\n* 498 ([[Wishaw]])\n* 867 ([[Denny, Falkirk|Denny]])\n* 1001 ([[Monklands (district)|Monklands]])\n* 1089 (7th [[Glasgow]])\n* 1138 ([[Ardrossan]])\n* 1153 (2nd [[Dumfries]]shire)\n* 1195 ([[Irvine, North Ayrshire|Irvine]])\n* 1271 ([[Bathgate]])\n* 1333 ([[Grangemouth]] [[Spitfire]])\n* 1371 ([[Girvan]])\n* 1701 ([[Johnstone]])\n* 1740 ([[Clydebank]])\n* 1777 ([[Dumbarton]] [[Blackburn Aircraft|Blackburn]])\n* 2166 ([[Hamilton, South Lanarkshire|Hamilton]])\n* 2175 ([[Hillington, Scotland|Rolls-Royce]])\n* 2296 ([[Dunoon]])\n* 2329 ([[Castle Douglas]])\n* 2414 ([[East Kilbride]])\n* 2452 ([[Shawlands Academy]])\n* 2496 ([[Cumbernauld]])\n}}\n;Northern Irish Squadrons\n* 72 (Omagh)\n* 806 (Larne)\n* 814 ([[Portadown College]])\n* 817 (Lisburn)\n* 825 (Bangor)\n* 833 (Antrim)\n* 1136 (South Belfast)\n* 1137 (East Belfast)\n* 1919 (Newtownabbey)\n* 2004 (Ballynahinch)\n* 2062 (Carrickfergus)\n* 2178 (Holywood)\n* 2241 ([[Regent House School]])\n* 2349 (Ballymena)\n* 2350 (Coleraine)\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== See Also == \n*[[List of squadrons in the New Zealand Air Training Corps| List of squadrons in the New Zealand ATC]]\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|http://www.raf.mod.uk/aircadets/|Air Cadets official 